comments: He has a very thick accent but you get used to it after a few weeks. He blew through the first half of the class in like two weeks which made it really difficult to understand anything , but after he realized he was going too fast he was a actually a decent teacher.

He is a good teacher. No fluff just material that you need to know. His accent is thick, but you understand him over time. I got a better grade in his class than the whole calculus series. I would take him again.
